an></h2>\n        <p class=\"text-lg text-teal-900/60 font-medium mb-12\" data-kid=\"152\" style=\"translate: none; rotate: none; scale: none; opacity: 0; transform: translate(0px, 40px);\">\n          Únete a los más de 500 establecimientos que ya optimizan su operación con StockyPOS.\n        </p>\n\n        <div class=\"flex justify-center gap-1 mb-12 h-12 items-center opacity-30\" data-kid=\"153\">\n          <div class=\"w-1 h-full bg-[#003B46]\" data-kid=\"154\"></div>\n          <div class=\"w-2 h-full bg-[#003B46]\" data-kid=\"155\"></div>\n          <div class=\"w-0.5 h-full bg-[#003B46]\" data-kid=\"156\"></div>\n          <div class=\"w-3 h-full bg-[#003B46]\" data-kid=\"157\"></div>\n          <div class=\"w-1 h-full bg-[#003B46]\" data-kid=\"158\"></div>\n          <div class=\"w-4 h-full bg-[#003B46]\" data-kid=\"159\"></div>\n          <div class=\"w-1 h-full bg-[#003B46]\" data-kid=\"160\"></div>\n          <div class=\"w-2 h-full bg-[#003B46]\" data-kid=\"161\"></div>\n          <div class=\"w-1 h-full bg-[#003B46]\" data-kid=\"162\"></div>\n          <div class=\"w-3 h-full bg-[#003B46]\" data-kid=\"163\"></div>\n          <div class=\"w-0.5 h-full bg-[#003B46]\" data-kid=\"164\"></div>\n          <div class=\"w-2 h-full bg-[#003B46]\" data-kid=\"165\"></div>\n        </div>\n\n        <div class=\"flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center\" data-kid=\"166\">\n          <button class=\"px-12 py-5 bg-[#003B46] text-white rounded-2xl font-bold text-lg hover:scale-105 transition-transform card-shadow\" data-kid=\"167\">Empieza Gratis</button>\n          <button class=\"px-12 py-5 border-2 border-[#003B46] text-[#003B46] rounded-2xl font-bold text-lg hover:bg-teal-50 transition-all\" data-kid=\"168\">Ver Demo</button>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</section>\n\n<footer class=\"py-20 bg-white border-t border-teal-50\" data-kid=\"169\">\n  <div class=\"max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-4 gap-12\" data-kid=\"170\">\n    <div class=\"col-span-2\" data-kid=\"171\">\n      <div class=\"flex items-center gap-2 mb-6\" data-kid=\"172\">\n        <div class=\"w-10 h-10 bg-[#003B46] rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center\" data-kid=\"173\">\n          <svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" data-lucide=\"package\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"lucide lucide-package w-6 h-6 text-white\" data-kid=\"174\"><path d=\"M11 21.73a2 2 0 0 0 2 0l7-4A2 2 0 0 0 21 16V8a2 2 0 0 0-1-1.73l-7-4a2 2 0 0 0-2 0l-7 4A2 2 0 0 0 3 8v8a2 2 0 0 0 1 1.73z\" data-kid=\"232\"></path><path d=\"M12 22V12\" data-kid=\"233\"></path><polyline points=\"3.29 7 12 12 20.71 7\" data-kid=\"234\"></polyline><path d=\"m7.5 4.27 9 5.15\" data-kid=\"235\"></path></svg>\n        </div>\n        <span class=\"font-extrabold text-2xl tracking-tighter\" data-kid=\"175\">Stocky</span>\n      </div>\n      <p class=\"text-teal-900/50 max-w-sm font-medium leading-relaxed\" data-kid=\"176\">\n        El ecosistema digital definitivo para la industria gastronómica. Nacido en Medellín, diseñado para el mundo.\n      </p>\n    </div>\n    \n    <div class=\"text-center md:text-left\" data-kid=\"177\">\n      <h5 class=\"font-bold text-sm uppercase tracking-widest text-[#66A5AD] mb-6\" data-kid=\"178\">Legal</h5>\n      <ul class=\"space-y-4 text-sm font-semibold\" data-kid=\"179\">\n        <li data-kid=\"180\"><a href=\"#\" class=\"hover:text-[#66A5AD] transition-colors\" data-kid=\"181\">Privacidad</a></li>\n        <li data-kid=\"182\"><a href=\"#\" class=\"hover:text-[#66A5AD] transition-colors\" data-kid=\"183\">Términos</a></li>\n        <li data-kid=\"184\"><a href=\"#\" class=\"hover:text-[#66A5AD] transition-colors\" data-kid=\"185\">Cookies</a></li>\n      </ul>\n    </div>\n    \n    <div class=\"flex flex-col items-center md:items-end justify-start\" data-kid=\"186\">\n      <h5 class=\"font-bold text-sm uppercase tracking-widest text-[#66A5AD] mb-6 invisible\" data-kid=\"187\">Social</h5>\n      <div class=\"flex gap-6 text-[#003B46]\" data-kid=\"188\">\n        <i data-lucide=\"instagram\" class=\"w-5 h-5 cursor-pointer hover:text-[#66A5AD]\" data-kid=\"189\"></i>\n        <i data-lucide=\"twitter\" class=\"w-5 h-5 cursor-pointer hover:text-[#66A5AD]\" data-kid=\"190\"></i>\n        <i data-lucide=\"linkedin\" class=\"w-5 h-5 cursor-pointer hover:text-[#66A5AD]\" data-kid=\"191\"></i>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 mt-20 pt-8 border-t border-teal-50 flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-between items-center gap-4\" data-kid=\"192\">\n    <p class=\"text-xs font-bold text-teal-900/30\" data-kid=\"193\">© 2026 STOCKY POS. TODOS LOS DERECHOS RESERVADOS.</p>\n  </div>\n</footer>\n\n<script src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/gsap@3/dist/gsap.min.js\" data-kid=\"194\"></script>\n<script src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/gsap@3/dist/ScrollTrigger.min.js\" data-kid=\"195\"></script>\n<script src=\"https://unpkg.com/lucide@latest\" data-kid=\"196\"></script>\n<script data-kid=\"197\">\n  // Inicialización robusta de iconos Lucide\n  function initIcons() {\n    if (typeof lucide !== 'undefined') {\n      lucide.createIcons();\n      console.log('Iconos inicializados');\n    } else {\n      console.error('Lucide no cargó a tiempo, reintentando...');\n      setTimeout(initIcons, 500);\n    }\n  }\n\n  // Ejecutar cuando el DOM esté listo y al cargar la ventana\n  document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', initIcons);\n  window.onload = initIcons;\n  \n  // Ejecución inmediata por si acaso\n  initIcons();\n\n  gsap.registerPlugin(ScrollTrigger);\n\n  gsap.to(\".widget\", {\n    y: \"-20px\",\n    duration: 3,\n    repeat: -1,\n    yoyo: true,\n    ease: \"power1.inOut\",\n    stagger: 0.5\n  });\n\n  const cards = gsap.utils.toArray(\".stacking-card\");\n  cards.forEach((card, index) => {\n    if (index === cards.length - 1) return;\n    \n    gsap.to(card, {\n      scale: 0.9,\n      opacity: 0.8,\n      scrollTrigger: {\n        trigger: cards[index + 1],\n        start: \"top 60%\",\n        end: \"top 20%\",\n        scrub: true,\n      }\n    });\n  });\n\n  gsap.utils.toArray(\"section\").forEach(section => {\n    gsap.from(section.querySelectorAll(\"h2, p, .bento-grid > div\"), {\n      y: 40,\n      opacity: 0,\n      duration: 1,\n      stagger: 0.1,\n      scrollTrigger: {\n        trigger: section,\n        start: \"top 80%\",\n      }\n    });\n  });\n</script>",
